title: Area Sports Calendar, 10/18/15
text: NOTE: Schedules provided by schools and are subject to change. TUESDAY High school volleyball: Nogales at Casa Grande Union, 6 p.m.; Empire at Vista Grande, 6 p.m. Junior college volleyball: Chandler-Gilbert at Central Arizona, 7 p.m. THURSDAY High school swimming: Casa Grande Union at Florence, 4 p.m. High school volleyball: Casa Grande Union at Catalina, 6 p.m.; Vista Grande at Flowing Wells, 6 p.m. FRIDAY High school football: Combs at Casa Grande Union; Vista Grande at Maricopa; Mission Heights versus Heritage Mesa at Carr McNatt Park; Florence at Coolidge; Santa Cruz at Valley Christian. All games begin at 7 p.m. High school volleyball: Vista Grande at Cholla, 6 p.m. Junior college volleyball: Central Arizona at Eastern Arizona, 7 p.m.
